extends basic.pug

block scripts
    script(defer, src='https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/d3/7.9.0/d3.min.js')
    script(defer, src='https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/save-svg-as-png/1.4.17/saveSvgAsPng.min.js')

    

block content

    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-sm-8 order-1">

            <div id="svg_chart">
                <button id="fullscreen-button" class="fullscreen-button" title="Fullscreen" aria-label="Toggle fullscreen" hidden></button>
                <button id="download-button" class="download-button" title="Download Image" aria-label="Download chart image" hidden>
                    <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                        <path opacity="0.5" fill-rule="evenodd" clip-rule="evenodd" d="M3 14.25C3.41421 14.25 3.75 14.5858 3.75 15C3.75 16.4354 3.75159 17.4365 3.85315 18.1919C3.9518 18.9257 4.13225 19.3142 4.40901 19.591C4.68577 19.8678 5.07435 20.0482 5.80812 20.1469C6.56347 20.2484 7.56459 20.25 9 20.25H15C16.4354 20.25 17.4365 20.2484 18.1919 20.1469C18.9257 20.0482 19.3142 19.8678 19.591 19.591C19.8678 19.3142 20.0482 18.9257 20.1469 18.1919C20.2484 17.4365 20.25 16.4354 20.25 15C20.25 14.5858 20.5858 14.25 21 14.25C21.4142 14.25 21.75 14.5858 21.75 15V15.0549C21.75 16.4225 21.75 17.5248 21.6335 18.3918C21.5125 19.2919 21.2536 20.0497 20.6517 20.6516C20.0497 21.2536 19.2919 21.5125 18.3918 21.6335C17.5248 21.75 16.4225 21.75 15.0549 21.75H8.94513C7.57754 21.75 6.47522 21.75 5.60825 21.6335C4.70814 21.5125 3.95027 21.2536 3.34835 20.6517C2.74643 20.0497 2.48754 19.2919 2.36652 18.3918C2.24996 17.5248 2.24998 16.4225 2.25 15.0549C2.25 15.0366 2.25 15.0183 2.25 15C2.25 14.5858 2.58579 14.25 3 14.25Z" fill="currentColor"/>
                        <path fill-rule="evenodd" clip-rule="evenodd" d="M12 16.75C12.2106 16.75 12.4114 16.6615 12.5535 16.5061L16.5535 12.1311C16.833 11.8254 16.8118 11.351 16.5061 11.0715C16.2004 10.792 15.726 10.8132 15.4465 11.1189L12.75 14.0682V3C12.75 2.58579 12.4142 2.25 12 2.25C11.5858 2.25 11.25 2.58579 11.25 3V14.0682L8.55353 11.1189C8.27403 10.8132 7.79963 10.792 7.49393 11.0715C7.18823 11.351 7.16698 11.8254 7.44648 12.1311L11.4465 16.5061C11.5886 16.6615 11.7894 16.75 12 16.75Z" fill="currentColor"/>
                    </svg>
                </button>
            </div>

        </div>
        <div class="col-sm-4 order-2">
            div(class='card')
                div(class='card-header') Forecast Symbol
                div(class='card-body')
                    <div id="symbol-selector" class='list-group'>
                        a(class='list-group-item list-group-item-action active', 
                        href='#', data-symbol='BTCUSDT', id='symbol-btc') 
                            strong BTCUSDT
                            br
                            small Bitcoin / USDT
                        a(class='list-group-item list-group-item-action', 
                        href='#', data-symbol='ETHUSDT', id='symbol-eth')
                            strong ETHUSDT
                            br
                            small Ethereum / USDT
                        a(class='list-group-item list-group-item-action', 
                        href='#', data-symbol='LTCUSDT', id='symbol-ltc')
                            strong LTCUSDT
                            br
                            small Litecoin / USDT
                    </div>

            include see_also.pug

        </div>

        <div class="col-sm-8 order-3">

            <div class="mt-5 py-2" >
                h2 Understanding Cryptocurrency Price Forecasts through Stochastic Modeling

                p In the volatile world of digital assets, predicting future price movements is both a challenge and a necessity for traders. This interactive tool provides a probabilistic view of potential price trajectories for major cryptocurrency pairs like <b>BTCUSDT</b>, <b>ETHUSDT</b>, and <b>LTCUSDT</b> using advanced stochastic modeling techniques.

                h2 How the Forecast works
                
                p Unlike traditional technical analysis that might point to a single target price, this forecast uses <b>Monte Carlo simulations</b>. By generating hundreds of potential random walks based on historical volatility and recent price action, the model provides a "cloud" of possibilities rather than a single line.

                h3 Interpreting the Visual Data
                ul
                  <li><b>The Mean Path (Dark Red Line)</b>: This represents the mathematical average of all simulated scenarios. It serves as the central tendency of the forecast.</li>
                  <li><b>95% Prediction Interval (Shaded Area)</b>: This band indicates the range where 95% of the simulated price paths fall. It represents a high-probability zone based on current market volatility.</li>
                  <li><b>Individual Forecast Paths (Colored Lines)</b>: These are single random-walk realizations. They demonstrate the inherent randomness and potential "noise" in price movements over a 7-day horizon.</li>

                h3 Interactive Features
                p This visualization is designed for deep analysis:
                <ul>
                  <li><b>Fullscreen Toggle</b>: Use the button in the bottom-right corner of the chart to expand the view, perfect for detailed inspection on any device.</li>
                  <li><b>Real-time Tooltips</b>: Hover over the chart to see the exact price values for the mean path and the upper/lower bounds of the prediction interval for any specific date.</li>
                  <li><b>Symbol Switching</b>: Quickly toggle between different cryptocurrencies using the selector on the right.</li>
                </ul>

                div(class="alert alert-warning mt-4" role="alert")
                    h4(class="alert-heading") Financial Disclaimer
                    p This tool is for <b>educational and informational purposes only</b>. The forecasts are generated by a mathematical model based on historical data and do not account for fundamental news, regulatory changes, or market manipulation.
                    hr
                    p(class="mb-0") <b>Trading cryptocurrencies involves significant risk.</b> Never invest more than you can afford to lose, and always perform your own due diligence before making any financial decisions.

            </div>
        </div>
    </div>